h1 Interviewing 101 

p.
  User research is not about asking our users what to build or do, and we would
  not build product that users simply requested without synthesizing and enriching
  that feedback with our own knowledge and perspective.

p.
  User research is about understanding their needs, pain points, and perspectives
  so we build better products that fit their mental model and their lives. 

